listing.title: Three Bedroom Town House, Arcadin, Arcadin, Athlone, Co. Westmeath
listing.seoTitle: Three Bedroom Town House, Arcadin, Arcadin, Athlone, Co. Westmeath
listing.description:
Arcadin is a brand new high quality development of 76 homes in a prime location with excellent transport links. The development contains a fine mix of house types with the final phase now being launched with a mix of 2 bedroom apartments and three bedroom townhouses.  

This is a well designed development with a very attractive site layout.   Designed by a local landscape architect, Arcadin incorporates ample green spaces surrounded by indigenous trees and hedges.

These exclusive homes will feature passive building methods at their very best reducing running costs and increasing efficiency for many years to come. Living spaces are thoughtfully considered in the design of these unique contemporary homes. Modern kitchens, branded integrated appliances including fridge freezer and dishwasher, spacious bedrooms, contemporary bathroom suites are all part of the offer .  

Location is unrivalled being a five minute walk from Athlone Town centre.   Local amenities include shops, chemists and a local injury clinic.   The local primary school is just a one minute walk from Arcadin.    The area is well connected to the transport network with bus stops minutes away and access onto to Galway - Dublin Motorway close by.
